name: Idea Lab
description:
What's an idea? Where is it's origin?
It's inception? It's start place and time?
The world of ideas, where are they born?
Are they carried in the air, lying on the surface, carried chaotically in the world of the unconscious?
Or maybe there are some secret laboratories of ideas?

Let's open the veil of mystery - neon lamps form real characters out of the colored chaos of the creative unconscious!
OK, ideas are already lit up and taking shape,
whose minds will pick them up? Who will think of them?
Maybe we already know some of these people?

There are lots of this idea labs, as cells in the human body,
there are many ways to find ones, but the main inspiration is what we find in meditation, music, inside ourselves or outside in the world.

So - Idea Lab - we are all in search - and may inspiration always be with us!
